Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:40.45,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Usoland nunca contaria uma mentira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.49,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Usoland é...
