Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:33.76,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Pare com isso, apenas pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:39.03,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Já chega, seus malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.70,Main,Gnomes,0,0,0,,Usoland!
